                     <h3>About Course</h3>
						<p>ALLEN CAREER INSTITUTE has established itself as a the prominent leader in the preparation for JEE (Main)/AIEEE. Year after year, it has given the best results in JEE (Main)/AIEEE. JEE (Main) courses designed by ALLEN are unique and are as per in sync with the latest examination exam pattern, which train the students to outperform in JEE (Main) exam. In order to draw the best out of the students and make them deliver top results, we provide the required guidance to the students. The JEE (Main) rank is based on the combined score of board exams and JEE (Main), so we have designed the course structure in a manner that supports students to perform up to the required standards in boards, as well as JEE. While designing the course, we focus on the theoretical concepts and practical problems; keeping in mind the changing patterns and trends in the competitive and school level examination.</p>
						<p>The practice material as provided by ALLEN is developed by our highly experienced subject experts, based on the extensive research and expertise of several years in the coaching of JEE (Main). The practice problems are designed in a structured and scientific way that facilitates the students to develop a complete understanding. We coach our students from the very grass root level and this enables them to achieve the best rank in engineering entrance exams.</p>
						<p>Since we value the significance of personal guidance in nurturing young minds to their absolute potential, we have made our classroom sessions for JEE (Main) course interactive so that they serve as a perceptive guide. We inculcate deep knowledge of the subjects in our students by means of our holistic approach. </p>
						<p>We believe that there is a champion in every student which needs to be discovered. ALLEN endeavors to discover the hidden champions, so it brings together the most renowned faculty, the most comprehensive course material, and the best teaching methodology. Periodic tests at ALLEN are rigorous and give an actual simulation of JEE (Main) and other top engineering entrance examinations.</p>
